." Manpage for ARCTIME.
.Dd 17 Oct 2016
.Dt "ARCTIME" "67" "Arc Utilites Library"
.Sh NAME
.Nm arctime
.Nd prints separate components of the date and time
.Sh SYNOPSIS
.Nm
.Op Fl dDMYTz
.Sh DESCRIPTION
The
.Nm
utlity uses a blend of BASh and AWK
to get the output of \fBdate\fP(1) and print out only
the components desired by the user.
.Sh OPTIONS
.Bl -tag -width flag
.It Fl d
Prints the abbreviation of the day of the week
.It Fl D
Prints the date
.It Fl M
Prints the abbreviation of the month
.It Fl Y
Prints the year
.It Fl T
Prints the current time
.It Fl z
Prints the time zone
.El
.Sh SEE ALSO
arcman(67), date(1), awk(1)
